---

# 6. Technologies Used

## Python

Python is the programming language used to develop the backend logic of the application.

## Flask

Flask is a lightweight Python web framework used to create routes, handle user requests, manage sessions, and connect with the database.

## SQLite

SQLite is a lightweight relational database that stores user account information such as usernames and password hashes.

## bcrypt

bcrypt is a password hashing algorithm that securely converts passwords into irreversible encrypted hashes with salt.

